subject: The Correspondence and Enqu
body:
The Correspondence and Enquiry Unit
1 Horse Guards Road
London SW1A 2HQ
General Enquiries
Attn: 
I hope you are well? can you let us know if our payment bank Leeds City Credit Union Bank UK has set up your Online Bank to enable you start initiating the transfer of your funds to any bank of your choice 
We await your urgent response.
Victoria Atkins MP
Financial Secretary to the Treasury

subject: Re:    The Correspondence and Enqu
body:
Hello Victoria Atkins MP,

I hope this message finds you well. I appreciate your prompt attention to my inquiry. Regarding the setup of my Online Bank with Leeds City Credit Union Bank UK, could you please provide me with more details? 

For instance, what are the steps involved in this process? And how can I ensure that everything is set up correctly? Also, could you tell me more about how the transfer of funds works?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Gretchen
